9bfd0a71c68d8f5220bed0","tid":2173146,"uid":34811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c28fbc0d186dad4ddd001e9f2e069d0d0119df0f","tid":2173146,"uid":81879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1770943bff2dbfa2ecaaf5281f9f05ac4e51a6ed","tid":2173146,"uid":63779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有少少慶幸，但一諗到有案底就。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:28:26.000Z","msg":"過咗感化就撤銷案底？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:46:31.000Z","msg":"之前睇過個話除咗簽保守行為，所有經法庭定罪嘅都會有定罪紀錄，但係罰款/判監唔過某個限額都可以話自己冇案底"}]}